 com anotações divididas por mês e ano. Ex: janeiro2020.txt, janeiro2021.txt, fevereiro2020.txt e etc. (0.2);</p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><span style="font-weight: 600;">Duplicar:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><li>Duplicar uma anotação existente (0.1);</li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exigências:</span></p><ul style="padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><li><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Utilizar o padrão DAO de persistência (0.1)</p></li><li style="margin-top: 0.25em;"><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Aplicar o paradigma O.O. Dica: Criar a classe Anotacao, criar a classe AnotacaoDAO e etc. (0.2)</p></li><li style="margin-top: 0.25em;"><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">utilizar e manipular o tipo data no python. ex: máscaras, formatações, validações e etc. (0.1)</p></li><li style="margin-top: 0.25em;"><p style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Interação com usuário (0.1)</p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><span style="font-weight: 600;">Prazo:</span>&nbsp;20/09</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;"=""><span style="font-weight: 600;">Valor:</span>&nbsp;2</p><p style="color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui="" variable",="" "segoe="" ui",="" system-ui,="" ui-sans-serif,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif,="" "apple="" color="" emoji",="" emoji";="" font-size:="" 16px;="" margin-bottom:="" 0px="" !important;"=""><span style="font-weight: 600;">Dica:</span>&nbsp;<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6996603/how-to-delete-a-file-or-folder" rel="nofollow" style="color: var(--color-text-link);">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6996603/how-to-delete-a-file-or-folder</a></p>', 2, 117, 1, NULL, false, true);
